Package: uncounted
Title: Estimation of Unauthorized Migrant Populations
Version: 2.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Maciej", "Beresewicz", , "maciej.beresewicz@ue.poznan.pl", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-8281-4301")),
    person("Aniela", "Czerniawska", , "anicze4@st.amu.edu.pl", role = "aut")
  )
Description: Estimates the size of unauthorized migrant populations using
    a power-law model that relates observed counts to reference populations
    and auxiliary detection data. Supports OLS, NLS, Poisson, and Negative
    Binomial estimation, alternative bounded detection links, optional gamma
    offsets, moment-based count estimators via the 'momentfit' package, and
    Bayesian Poisson and negative binomial workflows through optional 'brms'
    and 'rstan' integrations.
